---
title: Roasted Pesto Veggie Pizza with Mozzarella & Rocket
description: Add extra flavour to your vegetarian pizza by roasting the veggies first and tossing them with pesto – it ensures every bite is a tasty delight. Top the whole thing with lightly dressed rocket leaves for crunch and a fresh peppery flavour and you’ll never rely on takeaway again!
